      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait ibuprofen for the speech issue? i didnt think that would help. and caffeine? i thought that makes you more dehydrated. are you sure? it just feels like my head is spinning and i cant really focus on what i'm saying. its kinda scary, but i dont want to waste money on a doctor if it's just the heat. how much ibuprofen should i take to make the jumbled words stop?",
